{"tid":1971931,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】康復後肺部受創 美年輕律師：洗澡也站不起來","createTime":"2020-04-14T08:31:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-14T12:18:45.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"21f87df2111192b4f78597d041dde4e7143b1bf4","tid":1971931,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T08:31:20.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎令全球恐慌，皆因目前仍未找到疫苗或確實有效可治藥物，即使有幸治癒，也可能造成肺部損傷。紐約一名律師在3月中受到感染，情況一度嚴重至入住深切治療部，並插喉使用呼吸機。他現在痊癒出院，但生活完全改變，外出要坐輪椅，連洗澡也不能站太久。<br />\n<br />\n44歲的David Lat是法律網站Above the Law的創辦人兼編輯。他在《華盛頓郵報》撰文，講述呼吸機對武漢肺炎病人的重要性。他對當中情況十分了解，因為他曾確診武漢肺炎，入住紐約大學蘭格恩醫療中心（NYU Langone Medical Center）深切治療部，有6天要依靠呼吸機保命。<br />\n<br />\nDavid很清楚記得自己在3月16日因感染武漢肺炎入院，當時除了有感冒症狀，還有像哮喘一樣呼吸困難。他最初幾天情況穩定，只需額外氧氣幫助呼吸。但在3月20日傍晚，情況開始轉差。當晚醫生建議他插喉，使用呼吸機。<br />\n<br />\nDavid回憶表示，當時感覺驚慌。因為就在幾天前，他入院時，他父親曾告誡最好不要用呼吸機，因為使用的人最後都死亡。當護士準備為他插喉時，他一直想著不能死。他與丈夫還有一個兩歲的兒子，他要看到兒子高中、大學畢業。若兒子日後成婚有自己的子女，他也希望在旁見證。<br />\n<br />\nDavid形容使用呼吸機的整段時間都是在昏睡，完全不記得期間發生過甚麼的事情。幸好他在6天後可以自行呼吸，醫生就替他拆除呼吸機，但他的生活從此再不一樣。<br />\n<br />\n他的肺部須要重建呼吸功能。從前的他可以跑馬拉松，但現在即使是輕微活動，由房間一頭走到另一頭，或是上樓梯，也會氣喘連連。除非丈夫用輪椅推他出街，否則他無法到街口呼吸新鮮空氣。當他洗澡時，他無法一直站立，中途要坐在膠凳上休息。插喉接駁呼吸機亦令他聲帶受損，現在聲音非常沙啞，但言語治療師估計聲帶有機會好轉。<br />\n<br />\n全靠呼吸機David才能繼續生存，所以他呼籲政府要好好分配資源，讓每一個需要呼吸機的武漢肺炎患者，都會得到所需的治療，才可救回更多寶貴生命。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200414/large/1586843589_0245.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200414%2Flarge%2F1586843589_0245.jpg&h=4548cf06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200414/H5ROYUD3POK4VS3NJRQAPDSTOQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200414%2FH5ROYUD3POK4VS3NJRQAPDSTOQ%2F&d=lExWnqkLii2%2BVYlrfbo%2B85nDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=965a7027\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200414%2FH5ROYUD3POK4VS3NJRQAPDSTOQ%2F&h=6a0b81f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200414/H5ROYUD3POK4VS3NJRQAPDSTOQ/</a>"},{"pid":"35d060803d4cbb6fbd03219cb3769fcb53808c1e","tid":1971931,"uid":3454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T08:35:20.000Z","msg":"他與<span style=\"color: red;\">丈夫</span>還有一個兩歲的兒子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8372cfe9254348cedbe15d8acc7ef7f0b96db9af","tid":1971931,"uid":147721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T08:40:33.000Z","msg":"他父親曾告誡最好不要用呼吸機，因為使用的人最後都死亡。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f346ea4d53031fce562d7d9bfb2b3a912aadf40","tid":1971931,"uid":265134,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"35d060803d4cbb6fbd03219cb3769fcb53808c1e","tid":1971931,"uid":3454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T08:35:20.000Z","msg":"他與<span style=\"color: red;\">丈夫</span>還有一個兩歲的兒子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T08:41:43.000Z","msg":"咪戇鳩好冇？"},{"pid":"970de31ca86f2c94b7f952f094c21ebf34dc9189","tid":1971931,"uid":130626,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"35d060803d4cbb6fbd03219cb3769fcb53808c1e","tid":1971931,"uid":3454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T08:35:20.000Z","msg":"他與<span style=\"color: red;\">丈夫</span>還有一個兩歲的兒子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T09:04:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://davidlatcom.files.wordpress.com/2019/04/october-2018.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdavidlatcom.files.wordpress.com%2F2019%2F04%2Foctober-2018.png&h=e554db92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n全家福"},{"pid":"7043355887675eb29b8931ec6c75409429748bbf","tid":1971931,"uid":65201,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T09:08:12.000Z","msg":"好返又可以互射十次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cea651250540bd323a31de2a1f06e4f8fadfa19c","tid":1971931,"uid":55458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2f346ea4d53031fce562d7d9bfb2b3a912aadf40","tid":1971931,"uid":265134,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"35d060803d4cbb6fbd03219cb3769fcb53808c1e","tid":1971931,"uid":3454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T08:35:20.000Z","msg":"他與<span style=\"color: red;\">丈夫</span>還有一個兩歲的兒子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T08:41:43.000Z","msg":"咪戇鳩好冇？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T09:21:19.000Z","msg":"你咪戇鳩好冇？"},{"pid":"bc0dec4560e638a98468bc05e50d582a95a0ef15","tid":1971931,"uid":339053,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T09:21:28.000Z","msg":"佢唔武漢肺炎死, 都AIDS死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"842b099a9c685298c6aadb3370985817b2573019","tid":1971931,"uid":59328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T10:57:17.000Z","msg":"連登反同，條友應該活不久了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c267754d5c2664429f05c7f2818670e05e0efdc9","tid":1971931,"uid":34714,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T10:59:45.000Z","msg":"lgbt 一定係黃 🥺"},{"pid":"093bc1c3c1798d301982e7d6bc55c653402f64d5","tid":1971931,"uid":341865,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T11:01:03.000Z","msg":"D reply 低質到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c93582af1b2566fe21828a8207fd5094aac866c7","tid":1971931,"uid":55955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T11:01:16.000Z","msg":"生化武器<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2f3e0103dcf6eb1eaa2dd16ddf69158476b922c","tid":1971931,"uid":262093,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"093bc1c3c1798d3019